    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not even just the silence. it's the fact that everything feels... fake. i go to work, i buy groceries, i do all these things like they actually matter, but it's like i'm just a ghost going through the motions. he was my entire world. without him, i'm just this hollow shell. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but there's nothing left to wait for. everything just feels so pointless.",
